title: Exhaust Sound: MagnaFlow Cat-Back Exhaust on a Toyota Tundra
description: Make sure your truck has as tough a sound as the terrain it travels.

asset.title: MagnaFlow Toyota Tundra Cat-Back Exhaust System - Sound Clip
asset.description: MagnaFlow offers performance exhaust systems for the Toyota Tundra in both V6 and V8 that provide a deep, aggressive tone to give the 4.0 and 5.7 more room to breathe and more power. All MagnaFlow exhaust systems come with a Lifetime Warranty, and each kit includes all the necessary hardware and components for a complete, bolt-on installation. MagnaFlow products are proudly made in the USA. For more information, click here: http://bit.ly/1II5d8Q
